Class BodyParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.epitech.utils.BodyParser

  • public class BodyParser
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is used to parse body parameters. ex : "foo=bar&bar=foo" = {"foo" : "bar", "bar" : "foo"}
